{"tid":2169994,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你俾答案,我出條IQ題","createTime":"2020-08-23T02:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T03:30:26.000Z","uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"678ec7fea39eb5060e4857c38720e0e9d7595f6d","tid":2169994,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"一定好撚多陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe099df8cc61ba8c2374bdbfa46dd5e4620187c","tid":2169994,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"風間立花"},{"pid":"3dc1b3dd7f39dd030809325fa9cb36ff2c6d73d2","tid":2169994,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"Slut"},{"pid":"f4078751ef42141761bb51a4587d41a60c28b278","tid":2169994,"uid":246165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"因為外星人唔帶帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8378a23d65775f1d69ffb88a72dee9db26eb39a","tid":2169994,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"Rose ma"},{"pid":"2a639f6bb46ca8c668dce4671bdf2cb53616fef0","tid":2169994,"uid":40082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"觀自在菩薩, 行深般若波羅密多時, 照見五蘊皆空, 度一切苦厄.<br />\n<br />\n舍利子, 色不異空, 空不異色, 色即是空, 空即是色; 受想行識, 亦復如是.<br />\n<br />\n舍利子, 是諸法空相: 不生不滅, 不垢不淨, 不增不減.<br />\n<br />\n是故空中無色, 無受想行識, 無眼耳鼻舌身意,<br />\n<br />\n無色聲香味觸法, 無眼界乃至無意識界,<br />\n<br />\n無無明, 亦無無明盡; 乃至無老死, 亦無老死盡.<br />\n<br />\n無苦集滅道, 無智亦無得.<br />\n<br />\n以無所得故, 菩提薩埵, 依般若波羅密多故, 心無罣礙, 無罣礙故, 無有恐怖;<br />\n<br />\n遠離顛倒夢想, 究竟涅槃.<br />\n<br />\n三世諸佛, 依般若波羅密多故, 得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提.<br />\n<br />\n故知般若波羅密多, 是大神咒, 是大明咒, 是無上咒,<br />\n<br />\n是無等等咒, 能除一切苦, 真實不虛.<br />\n<br />\n故說般若波羅密多咒, 即說咒曰:<br />\n<br />\n揭諦, 揭諦, 波羅揭諦, 波羅僧揭諦, 菩提, 薩婆訶.<br />\n<br />\n摩訶般若波羅密多.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請出題"},{"pid":"78d3aa917bb396fc0642734c2702ebaec41f16da","tid":2169994,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"陳國邦<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9f7c44d7b55bdce975dec2e02175731f0bf9774a","tid":2169994,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"一蚊雞"}]}